column5: Poked around Toronto City Hall this evening. Lots of PanAm  stuff goin on. A PanAm volunteer comes over and holds out a tray of PanAm condomes free for the taking. Seems she thought i could use some. ? She said they have too many. I recall they ran out at the Vancouver Olympics. Had to get more. So I took a handful..... For souvenirs ?
You gonna go home and put on a moovee so you can test them out?
Seems she thought i could use some.   Missed opportunity?  Perhaps she was flirting.
did you get the complete set ? I think there were five, I grabbed them
What the heck??? are you kidding?  Really?
